articles.title: Jai Sri Ram India: David Warner sends heartfelt wishes after Ram Mandir Pran Pratishtha ceremony - India Today
articles.description: Australia opener David Warner took to Instagram to wish India after the Ram Mandir Pran Pratishtha ceremony. The IPL star shared a photo of Lord Ram on his social media page.
articles.content:
Australia's star opener David Warner extended his wishes to the people of India after the Ram Mandir Pran Pratishtha ceremony in Ayodhya on Monday, January 2022.
